4. User configures recurring bills in /expense/bills.
5. User posts occurrences when due to create transactions.
6. User sets monthly and category budgets in /expense/budget.
7. User creates goals and updates progress in /expense/goals.
8. User reviews reports and history in /expense/reports and /expense/history.

#### 5.6 Finance quick flows from dashboard
