## 10) Concept Coverage vs Planning Docs

Planning docs (plan.txt and NetWorthTracker.txt) describe a larger Life OS concept including:
- sleep tracking
- attendance
- life calendar
- broader journaling/media flows
- achievements and advanced analytics

Current shipped code focuses on:
- Tasks (strong)
- Finance/Net Worth (strong)
- Habits (basic)
- Notes (local-only)
- Task analytics and finance reports (partial)

So concept direction is clear and documented, while implementation is currently concentrated on productivity + finance core.

