## 11) Practical Readiness Assessment

### Good for now
- Single-user local use on trusted machine/network.
- Daily personal planning and personal finance tracking.

### Not ready for public deployment
- No auth, no user separation, no request controls.
- Inconsistent migration enforcement.
- Stale test scripts and partial feature wiring around recurring liability payments.

